4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed to equip individuals with foundational skills in cybersecurity, regardless of prior experience. Over 16 weeks, students attend three live online classes each week, with class sizes capped at 18 participants. The curriculum covers Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. Participants learn to manage risks using DLP strategies and comply with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, students receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. The program is available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop